summary.span: 定义可由 .NET 脚本引擎引发的异常集。

span.span: Defines the set of exceptions that can be thrown by a .NET script engine.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError AppDomainCannotBeSet = int32(-2146226176)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 无法设置应用程序域。Exception string: The application domain cannot be set. 由引发方法或方法时尝试都无法设置上托管的引擎，如 Visual Basic 或 JScript 脚本引擎的 AppDomain 选项。Thrown by the method or the method when attempts fail to set the AppDomain option on a managed engine, such as the Visual Basic or JScript script engines. 托管的脚本引擎不支持使用自定义应用程序域。Managed script engines do not support using custom application domains. 托管的脚本引擎将始终使用在运行的应用程序域。Managed script engines will always use the application domain in which they are running.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 指定的应用程序域无效。Exception string: The specified application domain is not valid. 由引发方法或时尝试设置不是有效的应用程序域引用的方法。Thrown by the method or method when attempting to set an AppDomain reference that is not valid. 若要重置`AppDomain`选项为空引用，调用方法。To reset the `AppDomain` option to a null reference, call the method.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError ApplicationBaseCannotBeSet = int32(-2146226174)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 无法设置应用程序基目录。Exception string: Application base cannot be set. 由引发方法或时尝试获取或设置 ApplicationBase 选项上托管的引擎，如 Visual Basic.NET 或 JScript.NET 脚本引擎的方法。Thrown by the method or method when attempts to get or set the ApplicationBase option on a managed engine, such as the Visual Basic .NET or JScript .NET script engines. 主机必须设置`ApplicationBase`在这将创建其脚本引擎的应用程序域中的选项。The host must set the `ApplicationBase` option in the application domain in which it creates its script engine.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError ApplicationBaseInvalid = int32(-2146226173)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 指定的应用程序基目录无效。Exception string: The specified application base directory is not valid. 由引发方法或方法尝试获取或设置 ApplicationBase 选项引擎和中的方法时指定为应用程序基目录的目录不是有效的目录。Thrown by the method or method when attempts to get or set the ApplicationBase option on an engine, and by the method when the directory specified as the Application Base directory is not a valid directory.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 程序集格式无效。Exception string: Assembly format is not valid. 当提供给的引擎的程序集无效时引发。Thrown when the assembly provided to the engine is not valid. 当一个引擎尝试运行或使用程序集时，通常会发生此异常。This exception typically occurs when an engine tries to run or use the assembly.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CachedAssemblyInvalid = int32(-2146226169)

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CallbackUnexpected = int32(-2146226168)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 无法在此时进行回调。Exception string: Callback cannot be made at this time. 由多个方法之一时引发的或在意外时调用回调方法。Thrown by multiple methods when one of the or callback methods is called at an unexpected time. 例如，由于调用引擎应该仅调用方法方法。For example, the method should only be called by an engine as a result of a call to the method. 如果调用在其他任何时间，则将引发 CallbackUnexpected 异常。If it is called at any other time, a CallbackUnexpected exception will be thrown.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CannotAttachToWebServer = int32(-2146226100)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 有效代码文档对象模型 (CodeDOM) 不可用。Exception string: A valid Code Document Object Model (CodeDOM) is not available. 由引发时属性不是可供读取的属性。Thrown by the property when the property is not available to be read. 引擎不支持属性或需要显式调用方法，以生成文档对象模型 (DOM)。The engine either does not support the property or it requires an explicit call to the method in order to generate the Document Object Model (DOM).

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError DebuggeeNotStarted = int32(-2146226114)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 调试目标应用程序未启动。Exception string: Debug target application not started. 当启动调试会话的 Windows 客户端时，由 aDTEngine.AttachDebugger 方法引发但`AttachDebugger`方法不能启动的目标应用程序与 TargetEXE 选项一起指定。Thrown by the aDTEngine.AttachDebugger method when a Windows client debugging session is initiated, but the `AttachDebugger` method is not able to launch the target application that is specified with the TargetEXE option.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 不支持使用调试信息。Exception string: The use of debug information is not supported. 由引发属性设置为 true，但是引擎时不支持的调试信息生成。Thrown by the property when it is set to true, but the engine does not support the generation of debugging information. 继续进行编译，但可以引擎编译代码，而没有调试信息。Compilation continues, but the engine compiles code without debug information.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError ElementNameInvalid = int32(-2146226164)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 异常字符串： 元素名称无效。Exception string: The element name is not valid. 由引发方法和方法时调用与名称参数无效，例如，一个包含无效的字符。Thrown by the method and methods when either is called with a name parameter that is not valid, for example, one that contains characters that are not valid. 请注意，主机必须不 ElementNameInvalid 时引发异常的 name 参数为 null 指针，因为 null 指针是用于请求引擎级数据的有效自变量。Note that the host must not throw an ElementNameInvalid Exception when the name parameter is a null pointer, as a null pointer is a valid argument used to request engine-level data.

Run 方法返回给调用方`GetCompiledStateFailed`异常返回`GetCompiledState`方法。The Run method returns to the caller the `GetCompiledStateFailed` exception returned by the `GetCompiledState` method. `Run`方法可能还会生成 GetCompiledStateFailed 异常，如果程序集缓存将引发异常。The `Run` method may also generate the GetCompiledStateFailed exception if the assembly cache throws an exception.
